title: Humanity Is Doomed - H3 Podcast # 245
description:
On this episode of the H3 Podcast OFF THE RAILS Ethan and the boys discuss Carl Tuck-da-dick's call to harass children, Joe Rogan's call for people not to get the vaccine, Caitlin Jenner running for office, and things get heated as the crew debates "Chair-Gate"!
  
 New H3 theme song by the amazing Otis McDonald available on YouTube and Spotify!
